Generates a set of tentacles for each speed set.

Author:
Adam Panzica
Parameters:
minSpeedThe speed of the slowest speed set
maxSpeedThe speed of the fastest speed set
numSpeedSetThe number of speed sets to generate
numTentaclesThe number of tentacles in each speed set
expFactThe exponential factor used to determine radius for each tentacle
resolutionThe resolution of the occupancy grid that the tentacles will be overlaid on
xDimThe length of the x-axis of the occupancy grid, in the positive x-direction and of the same units as resolution
yDimThe length of the y-axis of the occupancy grid, in the positive y-direction and of the same units as resolution
